111%2c%e8%81%b2%2c1702%2c20221003%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,聲,1702,20221003,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"聲","JNO":"1702","JDATE":"20221003","JTITLE":"聲請定其應執行刑"}